data.description: Step into the heart of West Palm Beach and discover your ideal residence! This 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom is perfectly positioned, offering the best of city living close to  City Place, I-95, the Outlet Mall, and markets  all while being within walking distance to the vibrant City Place and just a short drive to the sun-kissed beaches.Prime Location: Convenience is at your fingertips with easy access to major routes, shopping, and dining. Embrace the urban lifestyle by strolling to City Place for entertainment, restaurants, and boutique shops, or hop on I-95 for seamless commuting. markets  and the Outlet Mall are just around the corner, ensuring that your everyday essentials and shopping desires are effortlessly met.
